{
  "stem": "13382.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think that the strengths of the teaching, this was very weak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I found myself that I was really, most of the time, I was bored.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I learned much faster than the others, as well, I think most of the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- so we had no choice, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's what it was, I mean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The problem came, really, when you reach a stage to go to the high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then you had to leave town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was there no high school?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no high school in our place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the compulsory elementary school was four years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But 4 and 6 is 10 years. 10 years, child is still very little.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's very hard to let them go lose out of their parents' sort of supervision.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had five years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the class, it really was very boring.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we-- that was our life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we couldn't do very much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have-- especially children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next town was Lucenec, where there was a high school, two high schools, actually.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one which was in the lower grade, the other one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the people went to school, to Lucenec, because it was 15 kilometers by train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- [SIGHS] --my parents-- well, I say our parents-- would never agree to this arrangement, that we should travel into Lucenec, 15 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we have to get up early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the morning, we had to pray.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when you got bar mitzvahed, you have to put the tefillin on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what happens if you happen to sleep in?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then you-- either you don't pray, you don't pray that-- you turn to put the tefillin on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you go to-- to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
